    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Unpeaceful》是一款以战术对决与高速扩张为核心的即时战略游戏，节奏紧凑、对抗激烈。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每场比赛都从一片支离破碎的群岛展开，层层岛屿等待你征服，搭建桥梁、部署建筑、掌控关键资源，逐步扩张你的势力</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的军队由 <strong>Tapliki</strong> 驱动，它们虽小，却坚韧可靠，负责采集资源、建造设施并执行战场上的所有行动，能否高效调度它们将直接左右战局节奏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每张地图都拥有独特的经济与随机事件，不断变化的环境将迫使你调整策略、即时反应并精准执行，使每局对战都充满未知与挑战</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战前选择一项被动增益以强化你的优势，塑造属于你的战斗风格，让每一次开局都具备独特的战略味道</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 扩张意味着危险，摧毁敌方桥梁以切断他们的补给线，转瞬之间逆转局势，在这片群岛战场上，时机与地图控制就是一切</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>挑战好友进行正面对决，或踏入单人战役，迎击从异世界降临的神秘威胁。</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>高速且充满竞技性的 1v1 对决</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275980/extras/511b4fde2038feff543707c50e3f8c60.webp?t=1768560421\" width=800 height=20 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在快速而紧张的战术对决中击败你的对手，每一次决策都至关重要，每一秒都可能改变战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验精简却富有深度的 1v1 战斗，上手容易，但仍然提供足以左右胜负的战略空间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275980/extras/3d18e258d964bc1d1bf1ee12feafc241.webp?t=1768560421\" width=743 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>选择并建造你的建筑设施</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275980/extras/511b4fde2038feff543707c50e3f8c60.webp?t=1768560421\" width=800 height=20 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275980/extras/2d4e9066e37bd83fcd842cf1787af149.poster.avif?t=1768560421\" width=570 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275980/extras/2d4e9066e37bd83fcd842cf1787af149.webm?t=1768560421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在各座岛屿上部署设施，获取增益、强化关键位置，并解锁更多战术优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275980/extras/588994554ebaceae2ca3aaaedf68e6ae.webp?t=1768560421\" width=743 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>占领并掌控你的领土</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275980/extras/511b4fde2038feff543707c50e3f8c60.webp?t=1768560421\" width=800 height=20 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275980/extras/0c5340721da2aedce2af10478f4f1b81.poster.avif?t=1768560421\" width=570 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275980/extras/0c5340721da2aedce2af10478f4f1b81.webm?t=1768560421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">建造桥梁以夺取新的岛屿，每座岛屿都将提供独特的资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">摧毁敌方桥梁以夺走他们的岛屿，切断他们的通路，并让他们建造的结构反过来对付他们自己。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275980/extras/d75797c02890190980d1bd9ced7c7081.webp?t=1768560421\" width=743 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>释放神力</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275980/extras/511b4fde2038feff543707c50e3f8c60.webp?t=1768560421\" width=800 height=20 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275980/extras/b08f08a67ed2acc9e7020c40ab60ae9c.poster.avif?t=1768560421\" width=570 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275980/extras/b08f08a67ed2acc9e7020c40ab60ae9c.webm?t=1768560421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">呼唤远古神灵之力，重塑整个战场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">释放强大的能力，以强化你的经济、保护你的周围环境，或将敌人的策略反过来对付他们自己。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275980/extras/17c5770bc57e7ab1ec3822b4f5b8db19.webp?t=1768560421\" width=743 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>游戏一直都是人们放松身心、忘却日常烦恼的方式。</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>但如果来自异世界的麻烦突然跨越界限，直接降临在我们家中，会发生什么呢？</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
